@page "/"

<PageTitle>Puzzle Arcade</PageTitle>

<p>
  Choose a small puzzle game. Each game uses the same basic pattern:
  the player performs an action, the game updates its state, and the
  UI refreshes to show the result.
</p>

<div class="arcade-grid">
  <ArcadeCard Title="Word Guess"
              Description="Guess a hidden word using a limited number of attempts."
              Url="/word-guess" />

  <ArcadeCard Title="Number Logic"
              Description="Guess a hidden sequence of digits using clue-based feedback."
              Url="/number-logic" />

  <ArcadeCard Title="Grid Puzzle"
              Description="Click cells in a small grid until the board reaches a solved state."
              Url="/grid-puzzle" />
</div>
